parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Power steering failure can cause difficulty steering, making it hard to control the vehicle, especially in cold weather, which can lead to accidents or loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: power steering won't turn after initial start
steering wheel has a lot of play
morning sickness-like symptoms in the steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Power steering rack failure can cause difficulty steering, making it hard to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of vehicle control.
The failure of the aftermarket anti-theft device can cause a fire, resulting in damage to the vehicle and potentially putting the occupants at risk.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Slipping and Failure to Engage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and failure to engage can cause loss of control, accidents, and damage to the transmission, leading to costly repairs.
symptoms: Transmission slips and doesn't lock into gear
makes clunking sounds when acceleration is let off and then re-applied
transmission downshifts hard when accelerating from a sharp turn
vehicle suddenly accelerates or moves in an unintended direction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended vehicle movement can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities, especially if the vehicle is in park or neutral.
symptoms: engine revs and goes into reverse while in park
vehicle accelerates or moves in an unintended direction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the IAC system can cause the engine to stall or race, leading to loss of vehicle control, accidents, or engine damage.
symptoms: Engine RPMs increase when turning on the heater
engine RPMs remain high even after turning off the heater
engine races at high RPMs when putting the car in park
